      Nearest station: Old Street / Hoxton
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="imagetext__img lg:min-h-[450px]">
    {% rwdImg "/_assets/img/build/kingdom-code-build-st-johns-22.jpg", "Build at St. John's, Hoxton" , "(min-width: 640px) 50vw, 100vw", "imagetext__img" %}
