</section>

{% include "blocks/slider.njk" %}

<section class="imagetext imagetext--blue" id="sponsor">
  <div class="imagetext__text">
    <h2 class="uppercase text-2xl font-bold">Partner with BUILD</h2>
    <p class="my-2">From having projects to work on, through to covering the event costs, we need your help. The team give their time for free, but without the support of like-minded businesses, churches and charities, BUILD could not take place.</p>
    <a class="mt-2 inline-block hover:no-underline" href="/build/partnership">Find out more</a>
